            <lg xml:id="TK65">
<l>makkaṇmey tīṇṭa luṭaṟkiṉpa maṟṟavar</l>
<l>coṟkēṭṭa liṉpañ cevikku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To feel the bodies of one's children is sweet to the body; to hear</l>
<l>their speech is sweet to the ear.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
